## Phase 5: Integration Wiring

### 5A. Gift → Emote
In EmoteController KnitStart: listen to GiftService.Client.GiftReceived → auto-play "thank_you" preset.

### 5B. Co-op TD → Emote
In CoopTowerDefenseController: listen to WaveCleared signal → `EmoteController:PlayPreset("celebration")`.

### 5C. Co-op TD → Breeding
In CoopTDService: after WaveCleared, increment `VeteranWaves` attribute on surviving tower models. BreedingService reads this when constructing breed prompts.

