## Verification Plan

1. **Emotes:** Type emote prompt → verify LLM returns keyframes → verify animation plays on character → verify other players see it → verify preset emotes work without LLM call → verify content filter rejects bad rotations
2. **Gifting:** Spawn a creature → click Gift → select player → verify model transfers → verify GiftsGiven/Received increment → verify thank_you emote auto-plays on receiver
3. **Breeding:** Two players each spawn a creature → bring near each other → ProximityPrompt appears → both confirm → egg spawns with countdown → wait for hatch (use Cmdr to fast-forward time for testing) → hatch → offspring creature spawns with blended traits
4. **Co-op TD:** Switch to coop_tower_defense mode → join lobby → all ready up → waves spawn from multiple directions → towers attack → verify kill gold → gift a tower → wave clear triggers celebration → base destroyed shows game over
5. **Integration:** Gift tower in co-op TD → receiver gets thank_you emote. Breed veteran creature → prompt includes "battle-hardened". Wave clear → celebration emotes visible to all.
6. **Cross-platform:** Test all UI on mobile (44px touch targets), console (1.5x text), desktop. All buttons use .Activated.
7. **Linting:** Run `stylua .` and `selene .` after each phase.
